thread.title: SC

author: SC
title: SC
text: Very good service and the cards came out very nicely. The reason I am giving 4 stars instead of 5 is because I wanted to speak with someone about my card to see if I could change a portrait mode to landscape mode. It would be lovely if there was a number you can call. I tried something on the website with no avail. Sent an email to the team and till date no one has gotten back to me. Otherwise great service.
